data.title: Memoria Club 2018 19 Eng
data.meta_description: MEMORIA_CLUB_2018_19_ENG - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document provides details on FC Barcelona's 2018/19 season squad including the coaching team led by Ernesto Valverde and the medical team. It lists the assistant coach, technical assistant, goalkeeping coach, fitness trainers, scouts, material manager, and doctors, physiotherapists, and assistants that made up the medical team.
